    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anni ab incarnatjone eius millesimo
                        septuagesimo septimo et sedis domni <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/265"
                            >G(regorii)</persName> pape quarto, die vigesimo mensis februarii,
                        indic(ione) quintadetjma, <placeName ref="#places/1806">Arimini</placeName>.
                        Petimus a vobis domnus <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name
                                ref="Fuskinus Pomposianus">Fuskinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">mon(ac)h(us)</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui vocatur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pamposie</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartula libelli</rs>, nos quidem in
                        Dei nomine <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Sergius">Sergius</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Lisa">Lisa</name></persName> iugale mea
                        petitore seu filiis et nepotibus meis in duobus partibus et in alia vero
                        parte tertja <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martinus</name></persName> atque
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> cognatis
                        petitoribus cum nostris iugalibus seu filiis et nepotibus nostris − et si
                        quis unum ante alium obierit sine filio vel filia, eius porcio cadat ad
                        illos qui de nobis supravixerit seu filiis nostris − idest tres partes de
                        uno <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs> integro posito in <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters" ref="#estates/3939"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">Auguniano </placeName></geogName> et in fundo
                        <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Plebs
                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters" 
                            ref="#estates/3940"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Plebs
                                #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Casaria </placeName></geogName> quod fuit iure quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Benno">Benno</name></persName> et quondam
                            <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Arnaldus">Arnaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudice</rs>, cum ingressu et egressu suo et cum omnibus
                        sibi pertinentibus vel ubi de iamdicte tres partes mansi potueritis invenire
                        et per fundoras vel locas inquirere potueritis in fundo <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters" 
                            ref="#estates/3941"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Dolioni</placeName></geogName> et in fundo <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                    #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                    #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                    ref="#estates/3942"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                        #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                        #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                        >Rancomercolo</placeName></geogName> et in fundo <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                            ref="#estates/3943"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                >Metitulo</placeName></geogName> et in fundo <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                    #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                    #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                    ref="#estates/3944"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                        #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                        #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                        >Campolongo</placeName></geogName> et in fundo <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                            ref="#estates/3945"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                                #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                                #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                                >Foniano</placeName></geogName> et in fundo <geogName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                                    #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                                    #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                                                    ref="#estates/3946"><placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                                                                        #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                                                                        #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >Gualdo</placeName></geogName>. Hec omnia cum tegue et solamentis suis,
                            <rs key="#Canals">canal(e)</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> vero et <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">satjonabilibus</rs>, <rs>arbustris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs>, pomiferis et infructiferis,
                        posito in predicto fundo in <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/1806"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2434">Arimini</geogName></placeName>, in <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi #Fundi #Plebs
                            #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Hay/fodder #Forests
                            #Fruits/vegetables #Poultry #Pigs #Sheep #Exenia #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters" ref="#juridical_persons/3634">Sancti Laurentj qui
                            vocatur in Monte</orgName>, cum iustis et certis finibus. Nobis
                        suprascripti petitoribus seu filiis et nepotibus nostris predictam rem
                        habendum, tenendum, superhabitandum et in omnibus meliorandum in annis
                        continuis advenientibus numero viginti nove ad renovandum et caltjario
                        dandum. Et redditum reddere debeamus omnique anno, idest de omni <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">laboratjone maiore</rs> et in <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">minore</rs> modios quinto et pro salute in
                        Nativitate Domini scapula <rs key="#Pigs">porcine</rs> una et media et in
                        dominica quinquagesima tres <rs key="#Poultry">gallinas</rs> et in mense
                        martii tres partes de una <rs key="#Sheep">pecora</rs> et in Pascoa
                        resurrectionis uno <rs key="#Sheep">agnello et medio</rs>; alterius <rs
                            key="#Exenia">exenio</rs> vero de grano tres partes de uno quartario et
                        galina una et media et olne medietate et de vino due vegie et quartam partem
                        altera; hec omnia per nos vecturia in mansione vestra domnicata sine fraude
                        vel dolo aut malo ingenio. Maiore autem vestro domnico retjpiendo super area
                        et super <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">canales</rs> cum
                        honore et obedientja et pretjum exinde recepistis a nobis pro caltjario,
                        idest quattuor libras denariorum Veneticorum. Et minime habeamus licentjam
                        eam rem vendere vel donare ne commutuare neque per quodvis ingenium
                        extraneare et si oportum nobis fuerit quia nobis cumstare et auctoriare
                        promittistis cum tuis successoribus. Et si minime fecerimus et omnia ut
                        superius legitur non observaverimus daturi nos esse promittimus, pene
                        nomine, <rs key="#Penalty">auri untjas duas</rs> et post penam solutam
                        maneat libellum in sua firmitate, sub die et mense et indic(ione)
                        suprascripta. Signum manus Iohannes suprascripto confirmatore de omnia ut
                        superius legitur cui relecta sunt. Signum manuum Martinus atque Petrus
                        confirmatoribus de omnia ut superius legitur cui relecta sunt. Signum manus
                        Andrea de Mali[…] atque Azzolino sicque Rusticus de omnia ut superius
                        legitur rogati testes. <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> Ariminensis <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellio</rs> scripsi hec pagina.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
